# Photos collection
# 
# To add a photo, create a new Markdown file in this directory with format: YYYY-MM-DD-photo-name.md
# 
# Example file structure:
# ---
# layout: post
# date: 2025-11-05 00:00:00-0000
# img: assets/img/photos/your-photo.jpg
# description: Short description of the photo (optional)
# ---
# 
# Steps:
# 1. Add your photo image to assets/img/photos/ folder
# 2. Create a new .md file in _photos/ folder with the format above
# 3. Set the date, img path, and optionally add a description
# 
# Photos will be displayed in a responsive grid on the /photos/ page, sorted by date (newest first)

